# Cross-filter on a horizontal bar chart (no dimensions) emits the metric value instead of the x-axis category

### Bug description

Cross-filtering by x-axis value on `echarts_timeseries_bar` charts that have **no dimensions** (added in #37407 for #25334, and backported to 6.0 in #39913) does not work when the chart's **orientation is horizontal**. Clicking a bar emits a cross-filter whose value is the **metric (count) value** rather than the **x-axis category**, so every other chart on the dashboard is filtered down to zero rows.

The same chart with `orientation: vertical` works correctly.

